{"tid":1115331,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"7月24日 傑志對曼城 詳情公佈","createTime":"2019-04-19T06:04:00.000Z","updateTime":"2019-04-28T12:31:19.000Z","uid":36494,"like":2,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":21,"replies":[{"pid":"7ea928d2d5e9f6f216f768d47cab2703d92ef687","tid":1115331,"uid":36494,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-19T06:04:00.000Z","msg":"【傑志曼城 7.24 會師香港大球場 門票4.26開售】<br />\n<br />\n傑志正式宣佈，將與三屆英格蘭超級足球聯賽冠軍曼城合演季前熱身賽，比賽將於2019年7月24日晚上8時在香港大球場進行，是次賽事由成立45周年的EDPS電腦系統有限公司贊助，名為「賽馬會傑志中心盃」。<br />\n<br />\n是次賽事票價分為港幣$350、$590、$890、$1190，而學生及長者票價為$250。<a href=\"http://球迷可於4月26日早上10時起透過購票通網站www.cityline.com\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2F%E7%90%83%E8%BF%B7%E5%8F%AF%E6%96%BC4%E6%9C%8826%E6%97%A5%E6%97%A9%E4%B8%8A10%E6%99%82%E8%B5%B7%E9%80%8F%E9%81%8E%E8%B3%BC%E7%A5%A8%E9%80%9A%E7%B6%B2%E7%AB%99www.cityline.com&d=7%2FYu9khx8AV6Haip52opSWsgcJLaMXzh2FZp7TjlN88%3D&h=3dbe14b3\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">球迷可於4月26日早上10時起透過購票通網站www.cityline.com</a>、電話（2111-5333）或親臨香港大球場售票處（只限4月26日）預購門票。此外，4月27日起亦可透過其他購票通銷售點，包括通利琴行等親身購票。球迷每次交易最多可訂購6張門票。<br />\n<br />\n賽馬會傑志中心盃 Jockey Club Kitchee Centre Cup<br />\n傑志 Kitchee vs 曼城 Manchester City<br />\n日期 Date: 24/7/2019<br />\n時間 Time: 20:00<br />\n地點 Venue: Hong Kong Stadium<br />\n<br />\nTickets sales will be available on Cityline (Hong Kong) form 4.26!<br />\n================================<br />\n【會員買飛每張平HK$50!】藍浪一家球迷會門票預訂<br />\n<a href=\"https://bit.ly/2vhU4bz\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F2vhU4bz&d=7%2FYu9khx8AV6Haip52opSWsgcJLaMXzh2FZp7TjlN88%3D&h=615f8c41\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://bit.ly/2vhU4bz</a><br />\n<br />\n【傑志感謝祭開催!】18/19主場球衣低至$399<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.kitcheeonlinestore.com/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.kitcheeonlinestore.com%2F&d=7%2FYu9khx8AV6Haip52opSWsgcJLaMXzh2FZp7TjlN88%3D&h=e721355c\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.kitcheeonlinestore.com/</a><br />\n<br />\n【立即投票!】2018/19香港足球明星選舉<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.hkfa.com/vote\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hkfa.com%2Fvote&d=7%2FYu9khx8AV6Haip52opSWsgcJLaMXzh2FZp7TjlN88%3D&h=636abc56\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.hkfa.com/vote</a><br />\n<br />\n【傑志計劃選拔日】4月28 招收2004-2007出生學員<br />\n<a href=\"https://bit.ly/2UnIqGd\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F2UnIqGd&d=7%2FYu9khx8AV6Haip52opSWsgcJLaMXzh2FZp7TjlN88%3D&h=2eb95be0\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://bit.ly/2UnIqGd</a><br />\n<br />\n#wearekitchee<br />\n#同行壯志<br />\n#westandtogether"},{"pid":"42eaf07c1171477116f677da880d03317a21145d","tid":1115331,"uid":140834,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-19T06:09:33.000Z","msg":"暈浪一家都只係平50元<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/beat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e7223ca8145c8874e8868f3107b4619b498d2afb","tid":1115331,"uid":139573,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-04-19T06:11:38.000Z","msg":"費蘭度又可以單挑獲加<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/diu.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7ab38c9be6d6077c46bd99b4552b0a5fc90b6b13","tid":1115331,"uid":2502,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-19T06:31:25.000Z","msg":"四冠王<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/run.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ad4908b1062cb88a76ca7e602a56edf19d3b7cdd","tid":1115331,"uid":36494,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e7223ca8145c8874e8868f3107b4619b498d2afb","tid":1115331,"uid":139573,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-04-19T06:11:38.000Z","msg":"費蘭度又可以單挑獲加<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/diu.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-19T06:39:23.000Z","msg":"兩年後再遇"},{"pid":"ab68cad106b80a3071f9b0f023832b50b9035de9","tid":1115331,"uid":31923,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-19T06:44:57.000Z","msg":"炒到痴線<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"eae88d5cf98b4d3e